The paper discusses the development of a knowledge-aware recommender system, which involves the use of linked knowledge bases. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and databases (cs.DB) which are necessary for the development of such systems. Additionally, the paper involves some qualitative analysis experiments, which could also fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
